LayoutComposite

protected LayoutComposite(com.google.gwt.user.client.Element elem)
Creates a LayoutComposite with the given element. This is protected so that it can be used by a subclass that wants to substitute another element. The element is presumed to be a <div>.

Parameters:
elem - the element to be used for this panel.
